creator: wrowe@apache.org
text:
Which error log?  This certainly sounds like a bug for the 
  jakarta-tomcat-connectors team, not the httpd-2.0 server team.

  But I won't reclassify until you mention which error log, what other
  symptoms, etc.  Your report is insufficient to even identify a specific
  problem, never mind to solve it.

  Please reopen this bug with sufficient details - and we will try to help.
